abonminatrix,naladini,kokuryu,silverblads,nicaruveq,syllence 
<br />
sebbohnivlac,majestic,dalren,lildailye,stan,reanya,sympkynn 
<br />
aadorna,rixsar,maston,kirium,nitim,belgerion,rotlom,qurrgoth 
<br />
daybrighter2,zaniel,raura,xalmat,cyricus and everyone else
<br />

<br />
What I would like you to do is to review the list and comment on any 
<br />
tweaks that you feel need to be made before I send the list into Brenlo/Ash. 
<br />
Keep in mind that details will be provided to the developers explaining each topic.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal">Magician Top Ten List </span>
<br />

<br />
1.<span style="text-decoration: underline">Improve pets</span> (new detail provided) 
<br />
a)Damage ability (Stats/Hit consistancy+accuracy/damage crits) 
<br />
b)Survivability (SVstats/Mitigation) 
<br />
c)Utility (improved commands/procs/spells) 
<br />
d)Fix our lvl 51 and higher fire pets 
<br />

<br />
2. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Revamp pet focus availability</span> (new request) 
<br />
a)Summoners boon -Add quest version in tier 2 or equivalent zones 
<br />
for those w/o LDON 
<br />
b)Minion of darkenss - increase drop rate in Vex Thall, Add a quest in 
<br />
the new Veeshans Peak. Add the focus to Teir 3 PoP mob drops,Ex: 
<br />
First Sargents Insignia/Orb of Infinite Terror 
<br />
c)Introduce the Mancy (MoE level) pet focus into the elemental planes 
<br />

<br />
3. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Improve pet heals</span> (new detail provided) 
<br />
a)Shorter cast times, shorter recast times 
<br />
b)HoT, quickheal, CH spell options 
<br />
c)Have pet focus enhance pet heals 
<br />
d)Increase heal amount 
<br />

<br />
4. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Fix GoD Nuke Imbalance</span> (new request) 
<br />
This was caused from a missing GoD nuke. Mages are the only nuking 
<br />
class that was skipped for a GoD spell with a 20% increase to our FoT 
<br />
spell. OoW nukes now have a 30% increase to the GoD nuke which we 
<br />
never got. Instead this 30% is being now applied to our old PoP 2000 
<br />
nuke. Because this 30% is applied all nuking classes (including mages). 
<br />
Mages have now fallen far behind. This is should to be fixed. Our new 
<br />
OoW nuke should have 3120 damage in order to keep us balanced and 
<br />
even with the other nuking classes.  See this link: 
<br />
<a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=magicianbalance&message.id=1756" target="_blank">http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=magicianbalance&message.id=1756</a>
<br />

<br />

<br />
5. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Overhaul class specific AA's and Utility spells</span> (updated request)
<br />
    a)Elemental Agility- this AA is broken please fix it. Reduce AA cost by 2/3rds.
<br />

<br />
    b)Elemental forms- remove the levi component from Air form
<br />

<br />
    c)Add Quick Damage
<br />

<br />
    d)Add Improved Damage Shield
<br />

<br />
    e)Add Pet Convergence- innate ability (forces pet to attack one target till target is dead)
<br />

<br />
    f)Add Pet Control-innate ability (allows master to move pet with arrow keys) Ex C+arrow
<br />

<br />
    g)Fix Frenzied Burnout- 2-2.5 minute duration, add 2nd level cleave 3 and 100% pet crits add 3rd level double damage. 
<br />

<br />
    h)Host of Elements- increase hp make SV immune. Add other elemental forms (water,fire,air)
<br />

<br />
    i)Mend Compainion- Change this to a % heal of the pet's total buffed HP with 2 levels 75% cap and 100% cap (it is currently level of the magician X 33+1)
<br />

<br />
    j) Add Healing Adept and Gift, Advanced Healing Adept and Gift 
<br />

<br />
    k)Secondary Forte- decrease the cost of this AA from 15 to 10
<br />

<br />
    l)Shared health- increase range from contact to Line of sight
<br />

<br />
    m)Elemental Alacrity- lower cost to 3/3/3/3/3
<br />

<br />
    n)Elemental Fury- have crits apply to spells
<br />

<br />
    o)Servant of Ro- Add improved SoR pet charges and explodes on mob for 4500, 5500, 6500 DD.
<br />

<br />
    p)Refunds needed on Turned Summoned remove this AA please
<br />

<br />
    q)Add spells- Root, AE malosini, Group CoTH, Malos and Pet "kit" spells for targeted summons. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
6. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Update Rains</span> (new request) 
<br />
Remove the resists on Rains, and retune the mana cost on many rains 
<br />
"See <a href="http://www.magecompendium.com/editorials/rains.html" target="_blank">http://www.magecompendium.com/editorials/rains.html</a> for 
<br />
details". 
<br />

<br />
7. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Allow pets to live while the master is invisible</span> (new request) 
<br />
        (because we were told no on suspended pets zoning)
<br />

<br />
8. <span style="text-decoration: underline">COH useable in more zones.</span> 
<br />
Make CoTH available in all corpse summoning zones. If a small area 
<br />
of the zone is necessary to have both coth/corpse summon blocked 
<br />
for potential exploit reasons then just block that small area of the 
<br />
zone. 
<br />

<br />
9. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Upgrade our summoned items</span>. (updated request) 
<br />
a)Player equipable items should have OoW era focuses, stats and 
<br />
resists. 
<br />
b)Pet only items should have new procs like slow, snarelure and rune. 
<br />
c)Mage summoned augs should be created 
<br />

<br />
10. <span style="text-decoration: underline">Rathe's Son and the new OoW earth pet</span> (new request) 
<br />
Replace root with 100% snare to remove proximity aggro and 
<br />
breaking on nukes. 
<br />

<br />
Requests removed from top ten: 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">Targeted summons</span> (reason.. soon to be completed, developers are giving it to us prior to OoW) 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">MGB</span> (reason.. replaced with Improved DS AA) 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">Quick MGB</span>- (reason.. developers said not at this time) 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">Elemental Forms useable on mounts</span>.. (reason developers said not at this time) 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">Allow suspended pets to zone</span>.. (reason developers said possible in future expansion and we added the requests for pets to remain alive while master is invisible). 
<br />

<br />
-<span style="text-decoration: underline">Elemental pact</span>..(reason developers said no due to code issues)<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.cox.net/dtresendes/danisig.png" border="0" />
