				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">the list looks pretty good, but my only changes would be:
<br />

<br />
first to remove the 100% snare, if people really want earth pet to snare that's fine, but make it like 60%ish, there is absolutely no way anyone will ever get 100% snare period....asking for it is just gonna make the devs ignore the issue entirely
<br />

<br />
second we really need to push the issue of pets scaling with their masters gear, that's the only way pets are ever gonna be brought back into balance...otherwise pets are too powerful for newbie/twinks and too weak for high end mages. pet focuses given their rarity and the fact that they are a single item should be treated like nuke focuses...a nice bonus but not the main means of improvement. there is no reason a fresh recuit with pre-elemental gear that snags rotting qvic boots should have the same pet as a seasoned veteran in full tvexu level loot 
<br />

<br />
that's my 2cp...
